{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":7,"day":5}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"给肯尼迪画象（小演唱）","authors":["孙洪书邓兆雄"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"戊：（边打板边出）哎！人有脸，树有皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有脸皮的是肯尼迪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家要知道更详细，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看漫画肯尼迪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（向台内喊）同志们，给肯尼迪画象开始罗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（从锣鼓声中出，喊）好啊！戊：敲锣打鼓闹开台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白纸彩笔中间摆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪位画家先动手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把肯尼迪的丑象画出来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：海防战士武艺精，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写诗作画也能行；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管它豺狼多狡猾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士手下现原形！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戊：（白）谁开头？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（白）我先来，我来画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：（白）嗨！我先来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戊：（白）好！敲起锣鼓画起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：（画头发，唱）拿起这支笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来画肯尼迪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流线型头发抽象派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎呀！阿飞当中数第一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依得儿呀得儿哟哟哟哟哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀儿依得儿哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是从头坏到底！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看他，流线型头发盖脑袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他比艾森豪威尔更加坏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真备战，假和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反革命两手一起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（白）他左手拿着橄榄枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁：（白）开口派出和平队！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（白）和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁：（白）自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（白）平等，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁：（白）博爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（白）美元，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁：（白）（向丙要）拿来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（白）怎么，你也想上当？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（笑）哈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：他右手紧握火箭导弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁：穷凶极恶搞备战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：嗨！战争凶神肯尼迪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活象一只老狐狸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂脂抹粉把人迷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来画他的厚脸皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（画脸，唱）肯尼迪厚脸皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界数第一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴阳面是他的拿手戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（唱）呸！两面三刀他是个老狐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依得儿呀得儿哟哟哟哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀儿依得儿哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是世界人民公敌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：肯尼迪，家业大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在美国东部称一霸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手沾满了工人的血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剥削压榨发了家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看他，一半脸皮笑嘻嘻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肚子里净是坏主意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张脸上两副相，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地地道道的坏东西。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戊：（打板）对！我来揭揭他的老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"底。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肯尼迪，真疯狂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扩军备战搞得忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“有限战争”“核大战”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“特种战争”也在行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑动老挝打内战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"派兵又到越南南方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实行军事封锁古巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想在全球称霸王。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：听到这些气难消。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再把肯尼迪的嘴脸描。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（白）我来画！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（画眼，唱）左边眉毛高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右边眉毛低，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再加上两只三角眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎呀！眼睛一眨又出坏主意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依得儿呀得儿哟哟哟哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀得依得儿哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连忙派出U—2飞机。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（唱）本想搞情报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知糟了糕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"U—2飞机到中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白）轰——隆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（丙表演）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎呀，轰隆一声往下掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依得儿呀得儿哟哟哟哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀儿依得儿哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（丙画眼上绷带）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左眼贴上大药膏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：（画鼻，唱）鼻子真滑稽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：（唱）碰破了一层皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（唱）“共同市场”难开张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁：（唱）哎呀！“多边核力量”碰了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（唱）依得儿呀得儿哟哟哟哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀儿依得儿哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个鼻孔喘粗气！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（画嘴，唱）画上个大嘴巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露出大黄牙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屁股坐在火山口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎呀！嘴巴还说漂亮话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（白）他说什么呀？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：他说呀：俺有导弹核武器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力量总比世界人民大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（白）呸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（白）哎哎，哈罗，我肯尼迪不是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤立的，墨索里尼，希特勒，噢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"噢！还有东条，统统地支持我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的朋友——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（白）怎么样？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（白）——遍地下！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：啊？哈……哈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：牛皮吹不灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：纸老虎现原形。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：世界人民看得清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁：坚决打它不留情！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：打——打——打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：（画耳朵，唱）右耳被打掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：（唱）左耳往上翘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（唱）世界人民齐声讨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（唱）哎呀！它还假装听不到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依得儿呀得儿哟哟哟哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀儿依得儿哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（甲画当头棒打起的大包）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（唱）再给他一个当头炮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁：同志们快来瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它真相出现了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外强中干的美国佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"额上又加线两条。（画额线）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（白）哎！怎么突然老起来啦？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：嗨！肯尼迪是真霉气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：国内搞得乱吱吱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：到处是一片不景气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：工厂企业纷纷倒闭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：失业的人数往上加，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：生产的水平往下低，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：生产的东西卖不出去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：急得肯尼迪直"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓头皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：老板的利润大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大减低，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：直对肯尼迪来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发脾气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：（白）“肯尼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迪，你这个大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草包，你为什"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"么把经济危"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机又引来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说，你说……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：叫老板，你别"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这也不能全怪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：（白）笨蛋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（白）是老板。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：（白）草包！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙：（白）是老板。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（笑）哈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戊：哎，东风劲吹西风衰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸老虎画皮被扒下来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街老板发了慌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界人民喜开怀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（甲在肯尼迪象上加上红色大圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圈），"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：（唱）大家快来瞧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画得妙不妙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肯尼迪脑袋在当中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（唱）哎哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：（唱）射击场上当靶瞄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众：（唱）依得儿呀得儿哟哟哟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀儿依得儿哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看他能往哪里逃！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}